---
title: Sweet Chilli Beef Bao Buns with Crushed Spring Onion Potatoes & Slaw
description: Sweet chilli-glazed beef rissoles nestled within the fluffiest of bao buns - does it get any better than this? With the addition of crushed potatoes and a crunchy, crispy slaw, we can confirm it does!
